title: Michelle Keegan debuts stunning transformation at The BRIT Awards 2017 - but did you notice it?
text:
Michelle Keegan debuts stunning transformation at The BRIT Awards 2017 – but did you notice it? 
Actress changed her eye colour from brown to baby blue By Louise Randell, Senior Showbiz Reporter 22nd February 2017, 7:17 pm Click to share on Facebook (Opens in new window) Comments MICHELLE Keegan debuted a stunning new look at The BRIT Awards 2017 as she changed her eye colour from brown to baby blue. 
The actress stepped out wearing contact lenses for her big night at the O2 Arena in London. Getty Images 3 Michelle Keegan’s eyes have magically changed colour 
Michelle attended tonight’s glitzy prizegiving with her husband Mark Wright, but only eagle-eyed fans noticed her transformation into a blue-eyed babe. 
She seemed to have popped in contact lenses to change her brown eyes to match her bright blue jump suit. Getty Images Fans are more used to seeing Michelle with brown eyes Getty Images - WireImage
